		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />They usually take care of their stuff or the resellers only sell the stuff in good condition only.  The stuff sold abroad is usually the mint condition or something half mint that people wouldn't know the difference since they didn't saw how some stuff could be in good condition in the first place.
<br />
<br />If you go in the "junk" section, this is where you can find some loose VRC6/7 carts at 1$/2$ with may have connectors in no so great shape. So you have to look properly before buying. You can get at that price some just breed too if you search well.

		

